===Pronunciation===
אפרים / 'ephrayim / ef-rah'-yim

===Etymology===
Dual of a masculine form of {{HH|672}}; 

===Noun===
'''אפרים'''

# double fruit

===Proper noun===
'''אפרים'''

# Ephrajim, a son of Joseph; also the tribe descended from him, and its territory: - Ephraim Ephraimites

